{"tid":995191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長春鬧市發生爆炸","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T15:08:37.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e33ffad8d6187dc62905d0d38e55a250f3c90963","tid":995191,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/sh/2019-01-25/detail-ihrfqzka0974202.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fsh%2F2019-01-25%2Fdetail-ihrfqzka0974202.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=9I4BeS4eQ9jGYJ6jP2Db64zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ad14383c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/sh/2019-01-25/detail-ihrfqzka0974202.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n1月25日下午，吉林長春多名網友發佈視頻稱，紅旗街萬達廣場附近疑似發生爆炸，現場傳來「砰砰」聲。目擊者張女士告訴北青報記者，事發時她正在萬達廣場的一家餐廳吃飯，大約3點10分左右，突然聽到巨大的爆炸聲，「炸了有二十多下，商場廣播里說讓大家撤離，我們就趕緊跑出來了」。張女士稱，疏散時，有火星濺到她旁邊，但具體是哪邊爆炸、是否有人員傷亡暫不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n1月25日下午4時，北青報記者從長春市當地消防部門獲悉，目前消防人員已在現場處理，事發原因及是否有人員受傷的情況暫不方便透露。消防人員叮囑，當地市民請勿靠近事故發生地點，以確保安全。"},{"pid":"cab66a173f1952b01baa17e0d1d4566bda051ebb","tid":995191,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"哪有一天不爆炸"},{"pid":"9b877d6000fcc853b8ac17e93de76b55c35478c5","tid":995191,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:11:21.000Z","msg":"應節姐 有咩問題"},{"pid":"81be1007246a086d65704253436b5f7e582a115c","tid":995191,"uid":29982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"綠魔現身<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nX7e6LN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnX7e6LN.png&h=1c82b531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce6897b5a81c1a3cae4f296a66ef61582cd99a72","tid":995191,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"cctvb唔敢報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}